  "texts": [
    "One of the latest fields where biosensors have been incorporated is Ergonomics.",
    "The use of Explorative applications is recommended, so that users can move freely within the environment and so that the relationship between individuals and urban spaces can be assessed.",
    "EEG wearable sensors are recommended for evaluating the influence of spaces on cognitive processes.",
    "Eye tracking devices can be valuable for analyzing where the individual's gaze is fixated.",
    "Other complementary sensors, such as HR and EDA, can be included to gain a better understanding of user emotions."
